## ref vs reactive

```ts
// ref：可包任何值、用 .value 拿
const count = ref(0);
const name = ref('Nami');
console.log(count.value);  // 0
count.value++;

// reactive：只能包 object、不用 .value
const user = reactive({ name: 'Nami', age: 25 });
user.age++;

// 選用：primitive 用 ref、object 用 reactive
// 業界：reactive 比 ref 少坑（不用記 .value）
```

## computed — 自動算 derived state

```ts
const count = ref(0);
const doubled = computed(() => count.value * 2);
// doubled.value 自動更新
```

## watch — 監聽變化

```ts
watch(count, (newVal, oldVal) => {
  console.log(`count 從 ${oldVal} 變 ${newVal}`);
});

// 監聽多個
watch([count, name], ([newCount, newName]) => { ... });

// 深度監聽 reactive object
watch(user, (n) => { ... }, { deep: true });
```

## lifecycle hooks

```ts
onMounted(() => { /* component 掛載 */ });
onUnmounted(() => { /* 清理 */ });
onUpdated(() => { /* 每次 re-render */ });
```

## script setup syntax (Vue 3.2+)

```vue
<script setup lang='ts'>
import { ref, computed } from 'vue';
import ChildComp from './ChildComp.vue';

const count = ref(0);
const doubled = computed(() => count.value * 2);

// props
defineProps<{ title: string }>();

// emit
const emit = defineEmits<{ change: [value: number] }>();
</script>
```

2026 業界：所有新 Vue 專案都用 `<script setup>` + TS。

**☕ 用人話講**

Composition API 完全指南——把組件邏輯放進 setup()。**一句話記住**：像把相關工具放同一個抽屜——邏輯擺一起，大型組件好讀又好維護。

## Pinia 核心

```ts
// stores/user.ts
import { defineStore } from 'pinia';

export const useUserStore = defineStore('user', {
  state: () => ({
    name: '',
    age: 0,
    isLoggedIn: false,
  }),
  getters: {
    displayName: (state) => state.name || '訪客',
    isAdult: (state) => state.age >= 18,
  },
  actions: {
    async login(email: string, password: string) {
      const user = await fetch('/api/login', {
        method: 'POST',
        body: JSON.stringify({ email, password })
      }).then(r => r.json());
      this.name = user.name;
      this.age = user.age;
      this.isLoggedIn = true;
    },
    logout() {
      this.$reset();  // 內建 reset 到初始 state
    },
  },
});
```

## 用 Composition API 寫 Pinia (推薦)

```ts
export const useCounterStore = defineStore('counter', () => {
  const count = ref(0);
  const doubled = computed(() => count.value * 2);
  function increment() { count.value++; }
  return { count, doubled, increment };
});
```

## 在 component 內用

```vue
<script setup>
import { useUserStore } from '@/stores/user';
import { storeToRefs } from 'pinia';

const userStore = useUserStore();
const { name, age } = storeToRefs(userStore);  // 保持 reactive
const { login, logout } = userStore;  // actions 直接拿
</script>
```

## vs Vuex

- ❌ Vuex 5 種概念（state / getters / mutations / actions / modules）
- ✅ Pinia 3 種（state / getters / actions）— 拿掉 mutations、actions 直接改 state
- ✅ TypeScript 自動推導、不用寫一堆 interface
- ✅ DevTools 支援、time-travel debug

**☕ 用人話講**

Pinia——Vue 官方狀態管理（取代 Vuex）。**一句話記住**：像家裡的公佈欄——共用狀態集中放一處，而且比 Vuex 簡單九成。

## 業界常用 5 個 Composables

```ts
// 1. useLocalStorage
import { ref, watch } from 'vue';
export function useLocalStorage<T>(key: string, initial: T) {
  const stored = localStorage.getItem(key);
  const value = ref<T>(stored ? JSON.parse(stored) : initial);
  watch(value, (v) => localStorage.setItem(key, JSON.stringify(v)), { deep: true });
  return value;
}

// 2. useDebounce
export function useDebounce<T>(value: Ref<T>, delay = 300) {
  const debounced = ref(value.value);
  let timer: any;
  watch(value, (v) => {
    clearTimeout(timer);
    timer = setTimeout(() => debounced.value = v, delay);
  });
  return debounced;
}

// 3. useFetch (參考 vueuse 套件)
export function useFetch<T>(url: string) {
  const data = ref<T | null>(null);
  const error = ref<Error | null>(null);
  const loading = ref(true);
  fetch(url).then(r => r.json()).then(d => data.value = d).catch(e => error.value = e).finally(() => loading.value = false);
  return { data, error, loading };
}

// 4. useMediaQuery
export function useMediaQuery(query: string) {
  const matches = ref(window.matchMedia(query).matches);
  const handler = (e: MediaQueryListEvent) => matches.value = e.matches;
  onMounted(() => window.matchMedia(query).addEventListener('change', handler));
  onUnmounted(() => window.matchMedia(query).removeEventListener('change', handler));
  return matches;
}

// 5. useClickOutside
export function useClickOutside(target: Ref<HTMLElement | null>, callback: () => void) {
  const handler = (e: MouseEvent) => {
    if (target.value && !target.value.contains(e.target as Node)) callback();
  };
  onMounted(() => document.addEventListener('click', handler));
  onUnmounted(() => document.removeEventListener('click', handler));
}
```

**推薦套件**：`@vueuse/core` — 200+ 預製 composables、業界標配。

**☕ 用人話講**

Composables——Vue 版的 Custom Hook。**一句話記住**：像把常用邏輯錄成巨集——抽成 useXxx，多個組件共用。
